    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-103"><xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> que se usa para gestionar un evento; normalmente, se puede provocar desde el host o mediante el tiempo de ejecución como respuesta al caducar el temporizador de retraso.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-103">It is a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> that is used to handle an event; typically it can be raised from the host or by the runtime in response to a delay timer expiring.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-104"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> se hereda de <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SequenceActivity>; por lo tanto, se trata de una secuencia que cuenta con la restricción adicional de que la primera actividad debería ser <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-104"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> is inherited from <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SequenceActivity>; therefore, it is a sequence that has the additional restriction that the first activity should be an <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-105"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> es una <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, lo que significa que <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> puede contener otras actividades.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-105">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> is a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, which means the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> can contain other activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-106"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> es similar a la actividad <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SequenceActivity>, con algunas características adicionales.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-106">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> is similar to the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SequenceActivity> activity, with some additional characteristics.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-107"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> debe tener un elemento primario que sea <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ListenActivity>, <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateActivity> o <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-107">An <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> must have a parent that is either a <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ListenActivity>, <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateActivity>, or <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-108">El primer elemento secundario de una actividad <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> debe ser una actividad que se hereda de <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-108">The first child of an <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> activity must be an activity that inherits from <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-109">Todos los elementos secundarios subsiguientes pueden ser actividades de cualquier tipo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-109">All subsequent children can be activities of any type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-110"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity> bloquea y espera que ocurran algunos eventos pendientes, como el inicio de un temporizador o la llegada de un mensaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-110">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity> blocks and waits for the pending occurrence of some events, such as starting a timer or the arrival of a message.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-111">Cuando se produce el evento, <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity> termina de ejecutarse y, a continuación, se ejecutan todas las actividades subsiguientes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-111">When the event occurs, the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity> finishes running and then all subsequent activities are executed.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-112">Cuando <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> contiene una <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity>, <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> tiene algunas restricciones:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-112">When the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> contains an <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity>, the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> has some restrictions:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-113"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> puede contener una, y sólo una, actividad del tipo <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-113">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> may contain one, and only one, activity of type <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IEventActivity>.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-114"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> debe ser la primera actividad secundaria.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-114">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> must be the first child activity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-115"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> no puede estar en el controlador de eventos para una actividad secundaria y no puede ser un elemento secundario de <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> si <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> no es el primer elemento secundario.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-115">An <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> cannot be in the event handler for a child activity and cannot be a child to the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> if the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> is not the first child.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-116">Siempre que la primera actividad es <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity>, el controlador de eventos puede contener cualquier actividad.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-116">As long as the first activity is the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity>, the event handler can contain any activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-117">Si <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> contiene una actividad distinta de <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity>, esa actividad no puede tener un controlador de eventos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-117">If an activity other than <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> is contained in <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity>, that activity cannot have an event handler.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-118">Por ejemplo, se puede usar una actividad que admita el control de eventos dentro de <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity>, pero la actividad no puede tener los controladores de eventos asociados a ella misma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-118">For example, an activity that supports event handling can be used inside the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> but the activity cannot have event handlers attached to itself.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e61a3-119">Otro ejemplo es que <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> puede contener un <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup>, pero el <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup> no puede contener ninguna clase de <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e61a3-119">Another example is that the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> can contain a <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup>, but the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup> itself cannot contain any <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> classes.</span></span>  
  
   
  
